r any inconvenience. Sincerely, PayPal® Account Review Department PayPal Email ID PP4486 Visit our Privacy Policy and User Agreement if you have any questions. http://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr? cmd=p/gen/ua/policy_privacy-outside",1,phishyai
